        {
          "ruleId": "XSS",
          "level": "error",
          "message": {
            "text": "Reflected XSS in CSS context: the `comment` parameter is interpolated into a <style> block as a CSS property value at line 300 (`color: {comment};`). An attacker can close the style block and inject a script tag, e.g. `red}</style><script>alert(1)</script><style>`."
          },
