          }
        },
        {
          "ruleId": "XSS",
          "level": "error",
          "message": {
            "text": "Reflected XSS in HTML body via `comment` parameter: at line 310, the `comment` value is rendered directly inside a <div> (`Comment: {comment}`). This is a separate injection point from the `name` parameter, allowing independent exploitation through the comment query parameter."
